content:
=====
[[include component:preview
text=The bells hanging over the dusty doorway chime, as you push the creaking wooden door open. The dust settles, revealing a dark room, full of antiques, trinkets, rarities and more â€” all squirrelled away, hidden between broken lamps and scrap metal.]]
=====
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:blankstyle]]
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:queerstyle]]

[[module css]]
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dosis:wght@200..800&display=swap');

.echo {
    color: rgb(220 220 220);
    font-family: "Dosis", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8em;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 1em 0em;
    text-align: center;
}

body {
    background-image: linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        #1e1d1d, #5b535a 90px,
        #5b535a 90px, #715a6e 200px,
        #715a6e 200px, #937e90 100%);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

.licensebox p{
    color: black !important;
}

#page-content hr{
  background-color: white !important;
}

#page-content p{
    color: rgb(220 220 220);
}

:root {
  --fade-in-delay: 0s;
    --header-title: "Queerious";
    --header-subtitle: "LESBIAN TERROR";
}

.wrapHeader {
  font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  text-align: center;
  align-content: center;
  font-size: 1.5em;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  width: calc(80% + 10px);
  height: 50px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  background-color: #61412D;
  border-top-left-radius: 30px;
  border-top-right-radius: 30px;
}

.wrapHeader p{
  color: black !important;
  margin: 0;
  text-shadow: 2px 0 #ebb35a, -2px 0 #ebb35a, 0 2px #ebb35a, 0 -2px #ebb35a,
1px 1px #ebb35a, -1px -1px #ebb35a, 1px -1px #ebb35a, -1px 1px #ebb35a;
}

.wrapHeader a {
  color: black;
  text-shadow: 2px 0 #ebb35a, -2px 0 #ebb35a, 0 2px #ebb35a, 0 -2px #ebb35a,
1px 1px #ebb35a, -1px -1px #ebb35a, 1px -1px #ebb35a, -1px 1px #ebb35a;
}

.wrapHeader a:visited {
  color: #565656;
}

.yui-content p{
    color: black !important;
}

.wrapFooter{
  width: calc(80% + 10px);
  height: 40px;
  display: grid;
  margin-top: 0;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  grid-template-areas:
    "L-Foot Middle R-Foot"
    "L-Cap mid-gap R-Cap";
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 15fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: 4fr 1fr;
}

.L-Foot {
  background-color: #61412D;
  grid-area: L-Foot;
  margin: 0;
}

.R-Foot {
  background-color: #61412D;
  grid-area: R-Foot;
  margin: 0;
}

.L-Cap {
  background-color: #ebb35a;
  width: 80%;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;
  border-bottom-right-radius: 3px;
  grid-area: L-Cap;
}

.R-Cap {
  background-color: #ebb35a;
  width: 80%;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;
  border-bottom-right-radius: 3px;
  grid-area: R-Cap;
}

.wrapper {
  text-align: center;
  height: 636px;
  width: 80%;
  border: 5px solid #61412D;
  position: relative;
  /* 3D */
  perspective: 1000px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-areas:
    "top-left top-mid top-right"
    "mid-left mid-mid mid-right"
    "bot-left bot-mid bot-right";
  grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.wrapper > .top-left, .top-mid, .top-right, .mid-left, .mid-mid, .mid-right, .bot-left, .bot-mid, .bot-right {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  margin: 0;
}

.wrapper > .top-left {
  grid-area: top-left;
}
.wrapper > .top-mid {
  grid-area: top-mid;
}
.wrapper > .top-right{
  grid-area: top-right;
}
.wrapper > .mid-left {
  grid-area: mid-left;
}
.wrapper > .mid-mid {
  grid-area: mid-mid;
}
.wrapper > .mid-right{
  grid-area: mid-right;
}
.wrapper > .bot-left {
  grid-area: bot-left;
}
.wrapper > .bot-mid {
  grid-area: bot-mid;
}
.wrapper > .bot-right {
  grid-area: bot-right;
}

.panelBack {
  display: flex;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background-size: contain;
  position: absolute;
  margin: 0;
  background-color: #95867e;
  flex-direction: column-reverse;
}

.shelf {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 15px;
  background-color: #1b120d;
  margin-top: auto;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  margin-left: 0;
  margin-right: 0;
}

.door {
  background-color: #61412D;
  height: 100%;
  width: 50%;
  position: absolute;
  /* inner layout */
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-around;
  align-items: center;
  z-index: 3;
}

.left-door {
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  border-right: 1px solid black;
  /* transition */
  transform-origin: left;
  transition: transform 0.5s;
}

.right-door {
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  border-left: 1px solid black;
  /* transition */
  transform-origin: right;
  transition: transform 0.5s;
}

.shape {
  border: 4px solid black;
  width: 78%;
  height: 43%;
}

.knob {
  width: 17.5px;
  height: 17.5px;
  background-color: #ebb35a;
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 30px;
}

.left-knob {
  top: 48.5%;
  right: 8px;
}

.right-knob {
  top: 48.5%;
  left: 8px;
}

/* Door swing effect */
.wrapper:hover .left-door{
  transform: rotateY(-140deg);
}

.wrapper:hover .right-door{
  transform: rotateY(140deg);
}

/* Cabinet Items */

.queer_item {
  background-color: grey;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: auto;
  display: flex inline;
}

.qtTop {
  margin-top: 10%;
}
.qtMid {
  margin-top: 8%;
}
.qtBot {
  margin-top: 6%;
}

.queer_item > img {
  object-fit: cover;
  z-index: 1;
}

.queer_item > a > img {
  position: relative;
  object-fit: cover;
  z-index: 1;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.queer_hover {
  font-size: 1.1em;
  visibility: hidden;
  width: 75%;
  height: auto;
  background-color: black;
  border: solid #f737b0 2px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  position: fixed;
  z-index: 7;
  color: white;
  margin: 36% auto auto auto;
  padding: 10px 1em;
}

.queer_hover a {
  color: white;
}

.queer_hover a:visited {
  color: white;
}

.queer_hover hr {
  background-color: white !important;
}

.queer_item:hover .queer_hover {
  visibility: visible;
}

.mobileImage {
  display: none;
}

.defaultImage {
  display: inline;
}

/* MOBILE FORMATTING */

@media screen and (max-width: 800px){

.mobileImage {
  display: inline;
}

.defaultImage {
  display: none;
}

.wrapper {
  height: 90%;
  width: 90%;
}

.wrapHeader {
  width: calc(90% + 10px);
  font-size: 1.1em;
}

.wrapFooter {
  width: calc(90% + 10px);
}

.qtTop {
  margin-top: 40%;
}
.qtMid {
  margin-top: 35%;
}
.qtBot {
  margin-top: 32%;
}

.mblLeft {
  left: -5%;
}

.mblRight {
  right: -5%;
}

.top-left, .mid-left, .bot-left > .queer_item:hover .queer_hover {

}

}

.collapsible-block-folded > a.collapsible-block-link {
  color: white;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.collapsible-block-unfolded-link > a.collapsible-block-link {
  color: white;
  font-weight: 400;
}

.colSizeUp a.collapsible-block-link {
  font-size: 2.5em;
}

.collapsible-block-content > .blockquote p{
  text-align: initial;
}

[[/module]]
[[=]]
+ ##white|Welcome to the Cabinet of Queeriousities##
[[/=]]
[[div class="echo"]]
The bells hanging over the dusty doorway chime, as you push the creaking wooden door open. The dust settles, revealing a dark room, full of antiques, trinkets, rarities and more -- all squirrelled away, hidden between broken lamps and scrap metal.

What treasures can you discover here?

A woman with high cheekbones, long black hair, and wearing vintage clothing, coughs, grabbing your attention.

"Welcome to the **Cabinet of Queeriousities** -- I'm Queerious, the owner. Let me know if you need any help, or get lost, or hurt. Actually, don't tell me if you get hurt, I don't want to deal with the paperwork."
[[/div]]

-----

[[div class="echo"]]
"Oh, now those are beauties. My prized possessions -- everything you see in that cabinet is very important to somebody. I can't remember their name right now, but I'd know them if I saw them."

You sniff a pleasant cedar breeze, as the cabinet doors swing open. This must be a canon, you think.
[[/div]]

[[div class="wrapHeader"]]
[[[Forgotten Memories Hub| Forgotten Memories]]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="wrapper"]]
  [[div class="panelBack"]]
