    [[/div]]
    [[div_ class="knob right-knob"]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="top-left"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtTop"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Statuette%20of%20Harpokrates%20MET%20SF2316030.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/the-deadname-meme" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Statuette%20of%20Harpokrates%20MET%20SF2316030.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover mblLeft"]]
**[[[The Deadname Meme]]]**
-----
Heather Garrison is a new transfer to Site-43.
Dr. Lillian Lillihammer, her new boss, doesn't understand how Heather made an infohazard that can effect even her. Will she be able to explain her memeplex to her boss and maybe even come across as charming?
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="top-mid"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtTop"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Teotihuacan%20stone%20mask%20Soleil%20de%20nuit%20lot34%20n1.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-8688" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Teotihuacan%20stone%20mask%20Soleil%20de%20nuit%20lot34%20n1.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover"]]
**[[[SCP-8688]]]**
-----
A computer with anomalous compression. And that's just where this mystery starts. Heather is called in to help unravel the mystery, and it's way bigger than anybody expected.
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="top-right"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtTop"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Tecla%20Firm%20-%20Perfume%20Vial%20-%201981.74%20-%20Cleveland%20Museum%20of%20Art.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/the-lillihammer-test" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Tecla%20Firm%20-%20Perfume%20Vial%20-%201981.74%20-%20Cleveland%20Museum%20of%20Art.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover mblRight"]]
**[[[The Lillihammer Test]]]**
-----
Heather and Lillian partake in a journey through dreams and memories, as they undergo the Lillihammer Test. The test is simple, they take some hallucinogens, drugs that let them see each other's visions, and then just hang out and see what happens.
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="mid-left"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtMid"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Red%20Leather%20Notebook%20of%20William%20Clark.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/don-t-let-me-forget" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Red%20Leather%20Notebook%20of%20William%20Clark.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover mblLeft"]]
**[[[Don't Let Me Forget]]]**
-----
Heather's memory loss is getting worse. Lillian and Heather are getting desperate â€” so desperate that they're going to ask //Harry// for help. //Harry//.
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="mid-mid"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtMid"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Charles%20Le%20Bastier%20-%20Snuff%20Box%20%28Tabati%C3%A8re%29%20-%201957.406%20-%20Cleveland%20Museum%20of%20Art.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/love-between-the-margins" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Charles%20Le%20Bastier%20-%20Snuff%20Box%20%28Tabati%C3%A8re%29%20-%201957.406%20-%20Cleveland%20Museum%20of%20Art.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover"]]
**[[[Love Between the Margins]]]**
-----
This email is to announce that myself, Lillian Lillihammer, and Heather Garrison, are **romantically involved**.

Lesbians exist, I promise you.
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="mid-right"]]

  [[/div]]
  [[div class="bot-left"]]

  [[/div]]
  [[div class="bot-mid"]]

  [[/div]]
  [[div class="bot-right"]]

  [[/div]]
