[[div class="echo"]]
"Still don't have enough?" She says, noticing your gaze. "Try the next one. It's not the same collection, but they are all about the same things."

You look at the broken, leaning wardrobe beside you -- it pulses with an energy, feeling packed with emotions. They begin to flow through you, and you begin to feel nostalgic.

No, you realize, not nostalgic.

The **absence** of nostalgia.
[[/div]]

[[div class="wrapHeader"]]
[[[Forgotten Memories Hub| Forgotten Stories]]]
[[/div]]
