      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/RomanGoat.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/the-legend-of-the-iron-goat" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/RomanGoat.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover"]]
**[[[The Legend of The Iron Goat]]]**
-----
Heather Garrison used to work at Site-19, before she met Lillian. Dive into the world of a young Heather, as she tries to find her way alongside Luca Armaros, at the Site-19 Book Club!
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="mid-right"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtMid"]]

    [[/div]]
