      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Dice%20MET%20sf48-101-256a.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-7643" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Dice%20MET%20sf48-101-256a.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover mblLeft"]]
**[[[SCP-7643]]]**
-----
We've all been there right? Now which way did that door swingâ€¦
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="bot-mid"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtBot"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/1992_CollierTrophyGPS.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/reostiation" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/1992_CollierTrophyGPS.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover"]]
**[[[Reostiation]]]**
-----
Dr. William Wallace Wettle wasn't stupid.
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="bot-right"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtBot"]]

    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
