[[div class="echo"]]
The deeper you get into the shop, the darker it gets. Lanterns and art deco lamps light your path, as it weaves further and further back through the store. It seems to go on forever -- you wouldn't want to get lost!

A fanfare catches you off-guard. You turn to see a pair of red curtains. You begin to reach out towards them when, right before you can reach them -- the curtains separate, revealing another cabinet.

This one is on a stage.
[[/div]]

[[div class="wrapHeader"]]
Pseudogenesis Productions Presents
[[/div]]
[[div class="wrapper"]]
  [[div class="panelBack"]]
    [[div class="shelf"]]
    [[/div]]
