      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Gloves%20MET%20CI40.194.30dig.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-8478" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/Gloves%20MET%20CI40.194.30dig.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover"]]
**[[[SCP-8478]]]**
//Sense, A Pseudogenesis Production//
-----
A travelling theatre piece, focused on creating fully immersive experiences through cognitohazards. The first full introduction to a new GOI, Pseudogenesis Productions, an anomalous theatre company that is focused on safe, but transformational, experiences.
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="top-right"]]
    [[div class="queer_item qtTop"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/MedievalKey.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-8740" class="defaultImage"]]
      [[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/queerious/MedievalKey.png class="mobileImage"]]
      [[div class="queer_hover mblRight"]]
**[[[SCP-8740]]]**
//The Secret Project, A Pseudogenesis Production//
-----
Can we tell you a secret? We can't promise that it's our secret, but we can guarantee that not only are they all true â€” they will change your life.

A prequel to SENSE, exploring more of Pseudogenesis and the Foundation's response to an ambivalent, neutral anomalous theatre GOI!
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="wrapFooter"]]
[[div class="L-Foot"]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="R-Foot"]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="L-Cap"]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="R-Cap"]]
