[[/div]]

[[div class="echo"]]
You decide that, as fun as it would be to wait near the stage, in hopes of finding entertainment, there's more things to find. You look back from the stage and notice -- the room has changed. Unfortunate.

The deeper you find yourself in this rabbit hole, the more you are starting to understand. These trinkets, this collection of oddities and valuables, artworks and antiques; they are all memories. Or at least, they all lead to one.

You trip over a stack of magazines, knocking over a much larger stack, towering beside you. It falls to the floor with a dull thud. What do we have here?
[[/div]]
[[div class="wrapHeader"]]
//Anomalies// -- Foundation Papers
[[/div]]
[[div class="wrapper"]]
  [[div class="panelBack"]]
    [[div class="shelf"]]
    [[/div]]
