[[div class="echo"]]
Just as you are about to leave, you realize something. What if you never manage to find this store again? What if this was a fever dream and nothing is real? What if... what if you're just a character in the narration of an Author Page on a digital collaborative writing website, focused around speculative fiction, horror and, just maybe, romance too?

You shake your head. Of course not. That's stupid.

You notice that there are a couple of business cards scattered beside the doorway, resting on a short credenza. You grab one, and slip in into your pocket.
