[[tabview]]
[[tab About Me]]
Hey everybody! I'm Queerious, an author who cannot be contained. I like writing about weird memetics, girls, gay shit, and strange science crashing into culture and people. I've been slowly building out my repertoire on the SCP Wiki, and trying new styles out, so you'll never know what I've got coming next.

Between my series, my GOI, and my many, many, one-offs, I tend to keep my hands busy. On top of that, I'm a member of both moderation teams for the SCP Discord -- if you see me around, feel free to say hello!

Also I write about writing sometimes! Any essays I write about process are here:
[[[Cascading Story Arcs]]]
[[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/step-on-stones|To Step on Stones: Taking a Concept From Idea to Draft]]]
[[/tab]]
[[tab If I Disappear]]
[[<]]
If I ever stop posting or  no longer have activity on the official Discord server for a consecutive inactivity period of 3+ years, and if I cannot be reached through wikidot or Discord, my work rights go as follows:

